  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Rayman: Hoodlums' Revenge is an isometric platformer game based on Rayman 3: Hoodlum Havoc.\n\nA spin-off in the Rayman series, Hoodlum's Revenge takes place directly after the events from Rayman 3: Hoodlum Havoc and for the first in the series, aside from multi-player games, Rayman's friend Globox is featured as a playable character.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    },
    {
      "text": "After Rayman defeated the Hoodlums' leader, Andre, the Hoodlums decide do get revenge (hence the title), so they kidnap Rayman's best friend Globox. Rayman rescues Globox part-way through the game, and as the two of them find out more about the Hoodlums trying to clone Reflux, they decide to stop them for good this time.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb_storyline"
    },
